<main class="content">
	<article>
		<header class="head typo-l">
			<h2>Home</h2>
		</header>

		<div class="body typo-l">
			<p>Have you always looked for the chance to thank the people behind that cool project you always rely on, but never found the opportunity?</p>
			<p>Now you can, with <em>Dude, This Is Cool</em>: pick your favorite Github project/s and thank their author/s!</p>
		</div>

		{{#search-repo found_repo="transitionToRepo"}}
			{{#starred-repos}}
			{{/starred-repos}}
		{{/search-repo}}

		<section>
			<header class="notation">
				<h3>The freshest thanks.</h3>
			</header>

			{{#comments-list comments=latest_comments}}
			{{/comments-list}}
		</section>

		{{#github-auth}}{{/github-auth}}
	</article>
</main>
